;\"> <span class=\"c_t\"><a href=\"fsar/index.htm\">The Flying Saucers Are Real</a></span><br> by <span class=\"c_a\">Donald Keyhoe</span> [<span class=\"c_d\">1950</span>]<br><span class=\"c_b\">A classic of UFOology which slipped into the public domain</span>, and is also available in several formats from Project Gutenberg, based on this etext. </span> </p> <p> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('../cdshop/index.htm','cartwin','');\"><img src=\"../img/buycd.jpg\" height=\"20\" border=\"0\"></a> <span style=\"color: black;\"> <span class=\"c_t\"><a href=\"otof/index.htm\">Other Tongues--Other Flesh</a></span><br> by <span class=\"c_a\">George Hunt Williamson</span> [<span class=\"c_d\">1953</span>]<br><span class=\"c_b\">Another UFO classic which introduced many of the concepts of the field, such as 'walk-ins'.</span> </span> </p> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('../cdshop/index.htm','cartwin','');\"><img src=\"../img/buycd.jpg\" height=\"20\" border=\"0\"></a> <span style=\"color: black;\"> <span class=\"c_t\"><a href=\"sos/index.htm\">The Secret of the Saucers</a></span><br> by <span class=\"c_a\">Ofreo M. Angelucci</span> edited by <span class=\"c_a\">Ray Palmer</span> [<span class=\"c_d\">1955</span>]<br><span class=\"c_b\">By one of the first contactees, an inside view of the early UFO movement, and his visits to cosmic realms almost beyond human comprehension.</span> </span> <p></p> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('../cdshop/index.htm','cartwin','');\"><img src=\"../img/buycd.jpg\" height=\"20\" border=\"0\"></a> <span style=\"color: black;\"> <span class=\"c_t\"><a href=\"rufo/index.htm\">The Report on Unidentified Flying Objects</a></span><br> by <span class=\"c_a\">Edward J. Ruppelt</span> [<span class=\"c_d\">1956</span>]<br><span class=\"c_b\">The memoir of the US Air Force officer who coined the acronym UFO and spearheaded the early US Air Force UFO reports such as Blue Book.</span> </span> <p></p> <p> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('../cdshop/index.htm','cartwin','');\"><img src=\"../img/buycd.jpg\" height=\"20\" border=\"0\"></a> <span style=\"color: black;\"> <span class=\"c_t\"><a href=\"idtc/index.htm\">In Days To Come</a></span><br> by <span class=\"c_a\">Ashtar</span> (<span class=\"c_a\">Ethel P. Hill</span>) [<span class=\"c_d\">1957</span>?]<br><span class=\"c_b\">Please welcome Earth's new alien overlords....</span> </span> </p> <p> <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('../cdshop/index.htm','cartwin','');\"><img src=\"../img/buycd.jpg\" height=\"20\" border=\"0\"></a> <span style=",
